## 🚀 Application Overview

This application serves as a digital wallet allowing users to manage balances, convert currencies dynamically using real-time FX rates, and transfer funds globally. 

**Core Characteristics:**
* **Real-Time Reactivity:** Leverages WebSocket streams to push live balance updates and transaction notifications instantly to the client.
* **Financial Integrity:** Ensures ACID compliance for wallet debits/credits using strict transactional boundaries.
* **Modern UI/UX:** A mobile-first, highly responsive web interface utilizing signal-based reactivity for zero-jank rendering.

